Now you say,"Is it Ritambara Pragnya? Is it Bramha Shakti?

01:42:34.008 --> 01:42:37.553
Is it the all pervading power of Divine?

01:42:37.577 --> 01:42:47.179
Put a question to yourself three times.

01:42:47.258 --> 01:42:49.328
Now put your hands down.

01:42:49.353 --> 01:42:54.690
Check, whether you are getting cool breeze in your hands also.

01:42:54.714 --> 01:42:58.050
Now open your eyes. Open slowly

01:42:58.074 --> 01:43:01.910
and be in thoughtless awareness, don't think.

01:43:01.934 --> 01:43:06.437
Open your hands and check, if you are getting in your hands.

01:43:06.462 --> 01:43:10.051
Don't resist, it is a very subtle thing.

