01:43:32.393 --> 01:43:34.451
Those who have felt in hands, both the hands

01:43:34.476 --> 01:43:38.767
those who have felt cool breeze in hands and head or anywhere

01:43:38.792 --> 01:43:45.202
raise both the hands.

01:43:45.227 --> 01:43:47.682
Almost all of you have got it

01:43:47.706 --> 01:43:51.950
